data.description: Back on market, at no fault of the Seller. Beautifully updated 4 bedroom ranch with 1850 square footage! Unbelievable great/living room with over 500 sq. ft. will be the center point of this home and a great area to entertain. This room features a wood burning fireplace, newer flooring and a walkout to the covered patio. The updated kitchen has Pal Beach Dark Chocolate raised panel cabinetry, newer Wilsonart HD laminate countertops, ceramic tile backsplash and flooring. Both bathrooms have been updated. Formal living room converted to 4th bedroom would also make a great office. There is large laundry/mud room with newer flooring and cabinets. Carport was converted into large workshop/utility/storage room. The double driveway is an extra bonus.
